parameters.name: DedicatedHostClusterId
parameters.description: The description of the dedicated host cluster. It must be 2 to 256 characters in length. It cannot start with `http://` or `https://`.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The new name of the dedicated host cluster. The name must be 2 to 128 characters in length and can contain letters, digits, periods (.), underscores (\_), and hyphens (-). It must start with a letter. It cannot contain `http://` or `https://`.
